The Six Nations is the last competitive rugby tournament before England host the World Cup later this year.

The tournament begins on September 18 with England taking on Fiji at Twickenham.  

In 2014 Prince Harry was named as patron of the RFU's All Schools campaign, which aims to bring rugby to 750 more schools by the Rugby World Cup in 2019. 

